<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="author" content="Sunny Chung and Alan Mak">
  <title>Boozy Melts</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/styles/_header.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/styles/_footer.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/styles/boozy.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/styles/_back.css">
</head>

<body>
  <%- include('partials/_header.ejs') %>
  <%- include('partials/_back.ejs') %>
    <main>
      <div id="project1">
        <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/alan-mak/Moonfolio/master/images/boozy/BM_logo.png" alt="LOGO">
        <div>
          <h1>Boozy Melts</h1>
          <h2>Brand New Website Design</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/alan-mak/Moonfolio/master/images/project1.jpg" alt="Boozy Home Page" id="boozyimage">
      <div id="info">
        <section class="title">
          <div class="line"></div>
          <h1>Info</h1>
        </section>
        <div id="summary">
          <section>
            <h2>Overview</h2>
            <p>Boozy Melts is a local ice-cream store based in Etobicoke that serves alcoholic and non-alcoholic
              ice-creams.</p>
            <h2>Problem Statement</h2>
            <p>Boozy Melts currently does not have a website which causes users to have trouble looking for the menu, information about this restaurant and making purchases. <span>How might we design a website that helps users easily place an order and make it a delightful experience while using it.</span></p>
          </section>
          <section style="width: 25%;">
            <h2>Details</h2>
            <h6 class="detailTitle">My Role</h6>
            <h6>Research, Analysis, UX/UI Designer, User-Testing Facilitator</h6>
            <h6 class="detailTitle">The Team</h6>
            <h6>2 UX Designers</h6>
            <h6 class="detailTitle">Duration</h6>
            <h6>7 Weeks, October - December 2021</h6>
            <h6 class="detailTitle">Project Type</h6>
            <h6>School Project</h6>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="image-gallery">
        <section class="title" >
          <div class="line"></div>
          <h1>Prototype</h1>
        </section>
        <h3 class="title-highlight">Wireframes<section>Hi-Fi</section></h3>
        <section class="button-container"><a href="https://codesunny.000webhostapp.com/assignments/Boozy%20Melt/index.html" class="button">See My Prototype</a></section>
        <section id="image-cart">
          <div>
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/alan-mak/Moonfolio/master/images/boozy/Prototype/prototype_home.png" alt="home page">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/alan-mak/Moonfolio/master/images/boozy/Prototype/prototype_about.png" alt="About">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/alan-mak/Moonfolio/master/images/boozy/Prototype/prototype_faq.png" alt="FAQ">
          </div>
          <div>
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/alan-mak/Moonfolio/master/images/boozy/Prototype/prototype_flavour.png" alt="Flavour">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/alan-mak/Moonfolio/master/images/boozy/Prototype/prototype_cart.png" alt="Cart">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/alan-mak/Moonfolio/master/images/boozy/Prototype/prototype_ride.png" alt="Ride">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/alan-mak/Moonfolio/master/images/boozy/Prototype/prototype_time.png" alt="Time">
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
      <div id="design">
        <div class="title">
          <div class="line"></div>
          <h1>Design Process</h1>
        </div>
        <h3 class="title-highlight">Discovery</h3>
        <section>
          <h3>Research User Interview</h3>
          <div>
            <section>
              <h4>User Goal</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Order online</li>
                <li>Check what the restuarant offers and the ingredients of the ice cream</li>
                <li>Read comments and feedback from the previous customers</li>
                <li>Have a place to sit and hang out with friends</li>
                <li>Take photos at an aestheic place and post on socal media</li>
              </ul>
            </section>
            <section>
              <h4>Business Goals</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Attract more customers</li>
                <li>Increase revenue</li>
                <li>Provide taxi service (to increase more loyal customers)</li>
                <li>Provide a luxury service and experience</li>
                <li>Foster relationships and experience</li>
              </ul>
            </section>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/alan-mak/Moonfolio/master/images/boozy/Design_process/design_card.jpeg" alt="Group Card Sorting">
              <h3>Group Card Sorting</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <h3 id="card-caption">Participants Card Sorting</h3>
              <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/alan-mak/Moonfolio/master/images/boozy/Design_process/design_sorted.jpeg" alt="Participants Card Sorting" id="card2">
            </div>
          </section>
        <div id="define">
          <h3 class="title-highlight">Define</h3>
          <section>
            <h4>User Persona</h4>
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/alan-mak/Moonfolio/master/images/boozy/Design_process/design_user.png" alt="User">
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="ideate">
        <h3 class="title-highlight">Ideate</h3>
        <section>
          <h4>User Flow</h4>
          <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/alan-mak/Moonfolio/master/images/boozy/Design_process/design_flow.jpeg" alt="Design Flow">
          <h4>Information Architecture</h4>
          <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/alan-mak/Moonfolio/master/images/boozy/Design_process/design_IA.jpeg" alt="Architecture">
          <h4>Mood Board</h4>
          <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/alan-mak/Moonfolio/master/images/boozy/Design_process/design_colour.png" alt="Mood Board">
          <h4>Wireframes - Low Fidelity</h4>
          <div class="wrapper">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/alan-mak/Moonfolio/master/images/boozy/wireframe/Wireframe_about.png" alt="Wireframe About Us Page" class="wrapimg">
            <h5>Wireframe - About Us</h5>
          </div>
          <div class="wrapper">              
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/alan-mak/Moonfolio/master/images/boozy/wireframe/Wireframe_flavour.png" alt="Wireframe Order Page" class="wrapimg">
            <h5>Wireframe - Order</h5>
          </div>
          <div class="wrapper">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/alan-mak/Moonfolio/master/images/boozy/wireframe/Wireframe_time.png" alt="Wireframe Reservation Page" class="wrapimg">
            <h5>Wireframe - Reservation</h5>
          </div>
          <div class="wrapper">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/alan-mak/Moonfolio/master/images/boozy/wireframe/Wireframe_ride.png" alt="Wireframe Ride Service Page" class="wrapimg">
            <h5>Wireframe - Ride Service</h5>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
      <section class="button-container"><a href="https://codesunny.000webhostapp.com/assignments/Boozy%20Melt/index.html" class="button">See My Prototype</a></section>
    </main>
    <%- include('partials/_footer.ejs') %>
</body>

</html>